361
00:17:42,057 --> 00:17:42,818
Ok.

362
00:17:43,122 --> 00:17:44,408
Les Noirs ne sont pas drôles.

363
00:17:44,491 --> 00:17:45,928
Bien sûr que si, Keith.

364
00:17:46,039 --> 00:17:47,574
