377
00:18:40,887 --> 00:18:41,772
Oui.

378
00:18:42,532 --> 00:18:44,578
Super. Eddie ?

379
00:18:44,827 --> 00:18:45,850
Yo !

380
00:18:48,270 --> 00:18:49,694
La voici.

381
00:18:53,392 --> 00:18:54,388
Non.

